fields.name: <:TrainingCamp:497809297514692619> Personal Stats

fields.value:
`Global` / `G` - Leaderboard out of everyone using this bot.
`Verified` / `v` - Lists only verified users (**`\verify`**)
`Nofilter` / `nf` - Lists all users, no matter if verified or not
**You can combine some arguments:**
`\lb lvl9` - Level 9 Only.
`\lb ww v` - War Day Wins, Verified Only.
`\lb g ww l13` - Global, War Day Wins, Level13.
